Market: The geographical market where the EV battery design is being implemented, e.g., North America.
Feature_Percentage: The percentage of the EV battery design that features AI-enhanced battery management.
Reporting_Quarter: The financial quarter and year being reported, e.g., Q2 2025.
AI_Enhancement_Impact: A brief description of the impact of AI-enhanced battery management on the EV battery design.
Compliance_Status: Indicates whether the battery design is compliant with relevant regulations, e.g., EPA Greenhouse Gas Emissions Compliance.

AI_Enhancement_Impact: Basic AI features implemented for testing.
Minimal AI features with limited impact.
Minor improvements in charge cycle prediction.
Significant improvement in battery lifespan and efficiency.
Basic AI implementation for initial market feedback.
Improved charging times and better thermal management.
